   I do not as of yet know when I will be deleting my account so you may see a little of me online for awhile. I am trying to sell some of my things on my character in RL (not having much luck though), and I have to keep my account up till all that happens.<br>
   Fae, Once I have deleted my account I will remove all of my characters from Guild Magic, so I can be removed from the roster. However please, If you would allow me to continue having access to the guild forums that would be great, because I would like to keep in touch with all of you even after I no longer am playing. If that is possible, I thank you ahead of time. =)<br>
   I will miss you all very much. Good Luck in EverQuest and in RL all. <br>
<br>
Sincerely,<br>
Kigalan Wolfstar<br>
Forever a friend of everyone in Bloodsong<br>
